###       Test: /usr/share/tomcatX/carlos.properties exists
###       Action: Read existing DB credentials, verify schema is current, exit.
###       The postinst will handle minor patches if the build tag has changed.
###
###   (b) OSCAR 19 TO CARLOS MIGRATION — oscar.properties EXISTS, carlos.properties does NOT:
###       Test: oscar.properties exists; carlos.properties does not
###       Action: Set MIGRATE=true; read DB credentials from oscar.properties.
